                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I produce a certificate of Maynard's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted on the</hi> 29<hi rend="italic">th of May</hi>, 56<hi rend="italic">th Geo. III., of larceny in the dwelling-house of James Pitt, and transported for seven years.</hi>)</p>
               <p>(James Pitt was called, on his subpœna, but did not appear.)</p>
